title: Bobby’s Worries on Being A Dad + The Meaning Behind “4am Friend” and Who We Think Ours Would Be + Did Amy Let Her Daughter Watch Squid Game?

description:
Bobby shares a story about how people say their biggest accomplishments is their kids. He shares his worries on becoming a dad. A caller wants an update on if Amy ever let her daughter watch Squid Game on Netflix. We share the meaning behind a “4am Friend” and who we think ours would be.
